es speaking for various social and economic interests. As a result, the autocratic system of rule was undermined, and the fate of the political and social order remained uncertain.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 4aHistory -- European. 7aHISTORY / Russia & the Former Soviet Union.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080476697540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804766975423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804766975/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles